players.name: Cedric
players.bio: Cedric is a contender for league MVP, known for shooting, rebounding, and rim protection, he is a force to be reckoned with.

players.name: Kasch
players.bio: Kasch is a defensive monster known for great shot contesting and rebounding, he provides a constant threat on the defensive end.

players.name: Lachlan
players.bio: Lachlan is an aggresive offensive player known for his scoring ability and quickness, he primarily works in the paint.

players.name: William
players.bio: William is a versatile player on both ends of the floor, providing dunking, rebounding, and shot blocking.

players.name: Isaiah
players.bio: Isaiah is a quick and agile player known for his offensive firepower, he is a constant threat from the 3 point line as well as driving and dunking. Very clutch.

players.name: Jonny
players.bio: Jonny is a dominant force in the paint, known for his offensive rebounding and dunking, he also blinds his opponents with comedic quips.

players.name: Abel
players.bio: Abel is a powerhouse paint player. Masterfully backing down opponents and dunking on them. The closest comparison to Shaq in the league.

players.name: Clifford
players.bio: Clifford is an agile guard known for sneaking between defenders and dunking, he is also a great shot blocker and good at snagging steals.

players.name: Jude
players.bio: Jude is a versatile player with solid passing ability. He's quickly learning the game and should be someone to watch for in the future.

players.name: Nolan
players.bio: Nolan is a solid all around player, known for his 3 point shooting and fadeaways and defense, he is a constant threat on both ends of the floor.

players.name: Oren
players.bio: Oren is a high flying dunker with impeccable passing vision, he is a great team player and a constant threat on the offensive end.

players.name: Lee
players.bio: Lee is a high basketball IQ player, known for his great passing and court vision, he also is great at cutting off passing lanes and snagging steals.
